 Post "rave."Spook Country is the perfect follow-up to Pattern Recognition, which was called by The Washington Post (among many glowing reviews), "One of the first authentic and vital novels of the twenty-first century."', NULL, 2009, '1858788900', '9781858788906', 591, NULL, NULL, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/8355736-L.jpg', '/works/OL261552W', NULL, '2009', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'spook-country-william-gibson', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'import_only', '2026-03-16 14:53:11', '2026-03-25 00:23:59');
